Step 1:
Go to Spring initialzr : https://start.spring.io/
Add the following dependencies : Web , JPA , H2, MySQL
Generate the project and then extract it

Step 2:
Add the application.properties file in src/main/resources

Step 3:
Create the Model class (POJO) and add corresponding annotations and values(as mentioned in com.spring.jpa.model)

Step 4:
Add Dao interface and inherit CrudRepository

Step 5:
Add Corresponding controller and service methods

Step 6:
Run the application as Java Application from main class(com.spring.jpa)